HEADWORD: Frame-up
<hw>Frame"-up`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A conspiracy or plot for a
malicious or evil purpose;</def> <specif>especially</specif>, <def>an
act that incriminates a person on false evidence.</def>
